<inglise> In order to be officially recognized, a breeders' organization or association which maintains or establishes a herd-book must: </inglise>
<eesti> T&otilde;uraamatuid pidav t&otilde;uaretusorganisatsioon v&otilde;i -&uuml;hing peab ametliku tunnustamise saamiseks: </eesti>
<inglise> 1. have legal personality in accordance with the legislation in force in the Member State where the application is made; </inglise>
<eesti> 1. olema juriidiline isik vastavalt selle liikmesriigi kehtivale seadusandlusele, kus tunnustamist taotletakse; </eesti>
<inglise> 2. prove to the competent authorities: (a) that it operates efficiently; </inglise>
<eesti> 2. t&otilde;estama p&auml;devatele ametiasutustele, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (b) that it can carry out the checks necessary for recording </inglise>
<eesti> a) on v&otilde;imeline efektiivselt t&ouml;&ouml;tama; </eesti>
<inglise> pedigrees; (c) that it has a sufficiently large herd to carry out a breed </inglise>
<eesti> b) on v&otilde;imeline tegema vajalikku kontrolli p&otilde;lvnemise registreerimiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> improvement programme, or that it has a sufficiently large herd to preserve the breed where </inglise>
<eesti> c) tal on piisavalt suur kari t&otilde;uparandusprogrammi teostamiseks v&otilde;i tal on piisavalt suur kari t&otilde;u s&auml;ilitamiseks, kui see on vajalik; </eesti>
<inglise> this is considered necessary; (d) that it can make use of the livestock performance data necessary </inglise>
<eesti> d) saab kasutada t&otilde;uparandus- v&otilde;i s&auml;ilitusprogrammi teostamiseks vajalikke </eesti>
<inglise> for carrying out its breed improvement or preservation programme; </inglise>
<eesti> eluskarja j&otilde;udluse andmeid; </eesti>
<inglise> 3. have a set of rules covering: </inglise>
<eesti> 3. omama reeglistikku, mis h&otilde;lmab: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) the definition of the breed's (or breeds') characteristics; (b) the system for identifying animals; </inglise>
<eesti> a) t&otilde;u (v&otilde;i t&otilde;ugude) omaduste m&auml;&auml;ratlemist; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) the system for recording pedigrees; </inglise>
<eesti> b) loomade identifitseerimiss&uuml;steemi; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) the definition of its breeding objectives, </inglise>
<eesti> c) p&otilde;lvnemise registreerimise s&uuml;steemi; </eesti>
<inglise> (e) the systems for making use of livestock performance data, </inglise>
<eesti> d) aretust&ouml;&ouml; eesm&auml;rkide m&auml;&auml;ratlemist; </eesti>
